<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_556" id="277r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_556_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Awfſeſʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_556_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / von v̈lein helblıngs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l18"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> von dryſendorff etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l19"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> v̈lein helblıng <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> Oberſt ſchıerıſt ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wıl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l20">So ſol er vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu vnd von vns für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l21">on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> drey tag geleyt haben . Alſdenn <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır ſein rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l22"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l23"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Lucye </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_556" id="277r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Awfsesz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von Ülein
                                                Helblings <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                                Drysendorff etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>; und wenn
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Ülein Helbling
                                          <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">oberst
                                            schierist</q>06.01.1423</note></app> zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wil,
                                                so sol er umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> zu und von uns für
                                                uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                                  <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> drey tag geleyt
                                                haben, alsdenn <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                sein rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn
                                                wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Lucye. </ab>
</div>
